POWAMAIL

REQUIRE PHP 5.3+ ( BETTER 5.4+ )

REQUIRE BROWSCAP
REQUIRE PHP5-GEOIP AND A PROPER GEOIP DATABASE LIKE MAXMIND (city)

REQUIRE FILE LINUX UTILITY FOR UPLOADED FILE CHECKING (change the path in the file manager model )
REQUIRE spamassassin spamc e spamd (spamd listening on localhost)

EDIT THE URL IN THE CONSOLE/SERVICE/CONFIG/BOOTSTRAP, CONFIG/PATH AND PLUGIN/FILE_MANAGER/CONFIG/BOOTSTRAP
EDIT IN LAYOUTS BASE_URL

THE ATTACHMENT AND SANDBOX DIRECTORIES MUST BE ACCESSIBLE FROM THE WEB APP AND THE MAILER

[Thomas Schiavello Sviluppatore Software](https://www.thomasschiavello.it)
